titleStmt.title: Corpus parlamentar în limba română ParlaMint-RO
Romanian parliamentary corpus ParlaMint-RO
Stenogramele ședințelor parlamentului României
Meeting minutes of the Romanian parliament

respStmt.resp: Definirea etapelor proiectului și elaborarea caietului de sarcini.
Implementarea procesului de procesare a datelor și codarea corpusului în format TEI.
Data processing pipeline implementation, and encoding corpus in TEI format.

bibl.title: Meeting minutes of the Romanian Parliament

correction.p: No correction of source texts was performed.

normalization.p: Text has not been normalised, except for spacing.

hyphenation.p: Hyphenation has not been altered with respect to the source files.

quotation.p: Quotation marks have been left in the text and are not explicitly marked up.

segmentation.p: The texts are segmented into utterances (contributions) and segments (corresponding to paragraphs in the source transcription).

category.catDesc: acl: Clausal modifier of noun (adjectival clause)
expl:pass: reflexive pronoun used in reflexive passive
reparandum: Overridden disfluency (here used for program mistakes!)

prefixDef.p: URI-urile cu acest prefix indică numele elementelor. În acest document aceste URI-uri fac referință la categoriile din taxonomia UD-SYN.
Private URIs with this prefix point to elements giving their name. In this document they are simply local references into the UD-SYN taxonomy categories in the corpus root TEI header.

application.label: UDPipe
application.desc: UDPipe: a trainable pipeline for tokenization, tagging, lemmatization, and dependency parsing of CoNLL-U files. Pretrained model based on the UD Romanian RRT treebank, version 2.6.

application.label: Romanian ParlaMint lexical analysis pipeline
application.desc: Lexical analysis pipeline which applies UDPipe processing to each segment and saves the data into TEI XML format.
